<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UTKs LMS Account Activation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .activation-code {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .github-link {
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            display: block;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .github-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Account Activation</h1>
        <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>Welcome to my platform! To activate your account, please use the below code:</p>
        <p class="activation-code"><%= activationCode %></p> 
        <p>Please keep in mind that this activation code is valid only for 5 minutes.</p>
        <p>If you did not sign up for an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Thank you!</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/utk145" class="github-link">Explore more projects on GitHub</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
